    "title": "Canadian Syncope Risk Score",
    "desc": "The Canadian Syncope Risk Score predicts 30-day serious adverse events in patients presenting with syncope.",
    "data": {
        "orgreference": [
            {
                "href": "https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/27378464/",
                "text": "Thiruganasambandamoorthy V, Kwong K, Wells GA, et al. Development of the Canadian Syncope Risk Score to predict serious adverse events after emergency department assessment of syncope. CMAJ. 2016;188(12):E289-98."
